1
00:01:20,120 --> 00:01:21,440
Come on, come on!

2
00:01:21,960 --> 00:01:23,640
Come on, come on!

3
00:01:24,680 --> 00:01:25,680
Come on!

4
00:01:26,080 --> 00:01:27,240
Come on, come on!

5
00:01:27,240 --> 00:01:28,039
Come on!

6
00:01:28,039 --> 00:01:28,970
Come on, come on!

7
00:01:30,240 --> 00:01:33,440
Come on!

8
00:01:33,440 --> 00:01:34,960
Come on, come on, come on!

9
00:01:35,560 --> 00:01:38,800
Good job, good job!

10
00:01:39,160 --> 00:01:41,759
Dad, I won!

11
00:01:41,960 --> 00:01:44,360
You're the best, sweetie!

12
00:01:48,920 --> 00:01:51,160
Zhixia, get up!

13
00:01:51,240 --> 00:01:53,120
Shen Zhixia, stand up.

14
00:02:01,240 --> 00:02:03,360
When the you in two parallel timelines

15
00:02:03,360 --> 00:02:05,080
are dying at the same moment,

16
00:02:05,240 --> 00:02:07,800
one can sacrifice herself

17
00:02:07,800 --> 00:02:09,759
so the other can survive.

18
00:02:10,039 --> 00:02:11,800
She has made her choice

19
00:02:12,040 --> 00:02:14,320
to give the chance of life to you.

20
00:02:14,880 --> 00:02:16,720
You must make everyone who hurt her

21
00:02:16,720 --> 00:02:18,079
pay the price.

22
00:02:18,520 --> 00:02:19,840
Only by resolving regrets

23
00:02:19,840 --> 00:02:21,400
can you return to your own timeline.

24
00:02:21,400 --> 00:02:22,360
What regrets?

25
00:02:23,079 --> 00:02:24,810
Who should I resolve them with?

26
00:02:29,960 --> 00:02:30,760
Dad.

27
00:02:31,160 --> 00:02:32,280
Don't call me dad.

28
00:02:32,960 --> 00:02:34,760
I don't have a daughter like you.

29
00:02:35,160 --> 00:02:36,560
I went to great lengths

30
00:02:36,560 --> 00:02:38,290
to marry you into the Lu family.

31
00:02:39,400 --> 00:02:41,520
It's been a whole month,

32
00:02:41,800 --> 00:02:44,600
and you haven't even gotten into

33
00:02:44,720 --> 00:02:45,720
that Lu boy's bed.

34
00:02:45,720 --> 00:02:47,600
Aren't you completely useless?

35
00:02:48,320 --> 00:02:49,800
What's the point of raising you?

36
00:02:49,800 --> 00:02:52,329
What meaning does my marriage alliance have?

37
00:02:53,840 --> 00:02:56,480
I've raised you all these years for nothing.

38
00:03:01,680 --> 00:03:04,560
This... this isn't my dad.

39
00:03:05,000 --> 00:03:07,680
Is this another dimension?

40
00:03:09,800 --> 00:03:10,440
I don't know.

41
00:03:10,440 --> 00:03:11,480
He was beaten so badly.

42
00:03:11,480 --> 00:03:13,160
He was still unconscious when brought here.

43
00:03:13,160 --> 00:03:13,640
Really?

44
00:03:13,640 --> 00:03:14,840
It's terrible for a family to fight like this.

45
00:03:14,840 --> 00:03:16,040
They hit him too hard.

46
00:03:18,680 --> 00:03:19,560
I'm sorry.

47
00:03:32,400 --> 00:03:33,400
Shen Zhixia.

48
00:03:34,079 --> 00:03:35,000
He is...

49
00:03:35,720 --> 00:03:36,520
I'm sorry.

50
00:03:37,120 --> 00:03:38,880
Shen, how dare you hit me!

51
00:03:38,880 --> 00:03:39,840
Father-in-law,

52
00:03:42,440 --> 00:03:43,770
you have quite a temper.

53
00:03:47,320 --> 00:03:48,160
Sorry.

54
00:03:48,400 --> 00:03:49,520
I didn't see you.

55
00:03:49,800 --> 00:03:52,079
So it's my good son-in-law.

56
00:03:52,400 --> 00:03:53,200
Look at how

57
00:03:53,240 --> 00:03:54,760
this ungrateful wretch

58
00:03:55,280 --> 00:03:56,640
beat me up like this.

59
00:03:56,640 --> 00:03:58,240
How dare you play the victim.

60
00:03:58,320 --> 00:03:59,680
You clearly started it.

61
00:03:59,680 --> 00:04:00,680
So what if I hit you?

62
00:04:00,680 --> 00:04:02,600
I don't need a special day to hit you.

63
00:04:02,600 --> 00:04:04,080
Say something.

64
00:04:04,080 --> 00:04:04,880
You.

65
00:04:08,960 --> 00:04:11,280
How dare you fight back.

66
00:04:11,760 --> 00:04:12,680
Just you wait.

67
00:04:12,800 --> 00:04:14,720
I will break your legs today.

68
00:04:17,200 --> 00:04:18,079
Don't dodge.

69
00:04:23,200 --> 00:04:24,680
Am I imagining things?

70
00:04:24,720 --> 00:04:27,240
Why do I feel like she's a different person?

71
00:04:28,040 --> 00:04:29,440
What is coming out of

72
00:04:29,440 --> 00:04:31,080
this unrighteous mouth?

73
00:04:31,280 --> 00:04:32,880
Everyone heard it.

74
00:04:32,880 --> 00:04:34,240
This is the good daughter of our Shen family.

75
00:04:34,240 --> 00:04:34,680
You...

76
00:04:34,960 --> 00:04:35,680
Enough.

77
00:04:37,040 --> 00:04:39,760
I don't care if the Shen family has no shame.

78
00:04:39,840 --> 00:04:40,800
But now,

79
00:04:41,120 --> 00:04:43,159
Shen Zhixia is my wife.

80
00:04:44,240 --> 00:04:47,520
Hitting someone from the Lu family is slapping the Lu family in the face.

81
00:04:47,520 --> 00:04:50,720
Do I need to remind you of this, Father-in-law?

82
00:04:53,280 --> 00:04:54,120
Come home with me.

83
00:04:54,120 --> 00:04:54,880
Go home?

84
00:04:56,159 --> 00:04:57,720
I don't think that's a good idea.

85
00:04:57,720 --> 00:04:58,520
Lu Jingheng,

86
00:04:58,720 --> 00:05:00,320
put me down! Lu Jingheng!

87
00:05:00,720 --> 00:05:01,880
Let me go.

88
00:05:02,520 --> 00:05:03,600
Let me go.

89
00:05:11,440 --> 00:05:12,440
Get out of the car.

90
00:05:13,720 --> 00:05:15,000
I want to go back to the Shens'.

91
00:05:15,000 --> 00:05:15,760
Who was the one

92
00:05:15,760 --> 00:05:17,280
who tried so hard to marry into the Lu family?

93
00:05:17,280 --> 00:05:18,200
I can tell.

94
00:05:18,200 --> 00:05:19,920
You look down on me, right?

95
00:05:19,920 --> 00:05:20,640
Let me tell you,

96
00:05:20,640 --> 00:05:22,720
go find whoever forced you into this marriage.

97
00:05:22,720 --> 00:05:23,920
This marriage is what

98
00:05:24,160 --> 00:05:26,400
your Shen family desperately begged for.

99
00:05:26,400 --> 00:05:28,040
If you are not willing, neither am I.

100
00:05:28,040 --> 00:05:28,920
I'm telling you,

101
00:05:28,920 --> 00:05:30,120
we will get divorced tomorrow.

102
00:05:30,120 --> 00:05:31,250
I will make it quick.

103
00:05:31,800 --> 00:05:32,860
What are you doing?

104
00:05:32,960 --> 00:05:35,480
Are you playing the domineering CEO forcing his love on me?

105
00:05:35,480 --> 00:05:37,640
I haven't rehearsed this.

106
00:05:37,920 --> 00:05:38,720
Go away.

107
00:05:39,600 --> 00:05:40,440
Shen Zhixia.

108
00:05:41,120 --> 00:05:42,920
Just try mentioning divorce one more time.

109
00:05:42,920 --> 00:05:45,159
This marriage was just a deal to begin with.

110
00:05:45,159 --> 00:05:47,120
Shen Zhixia, remember this.

111
00:05:47,360 --> 00:05:48,400
You are mine.

112
00:05:49,120 --> 00:05:50,240
If you want a divorce,

113
00:05:50,240 --> 00:05:51,770
it will be over my dead body.

114
00:05:58,440 --> 00:05:59,440
Go away.

115
00:06:00,120 --> 00:06:01,720
No, I'm done rehearsing.

116
00:06:01,880 --> 00:06:03,280
You don't want to act anymore, right?

117
00:06:03,280 --> 00:06:04,080
Divorce.

118
00:06:04,680 --> 00:06:06,340
You had better keep your word.

119
00:06:08,800 --> 00:06:09,680
Young Master.

120
00:06:15,280 --> 00:06:17,320
You must make everyone who hurt her

121
00:06:17,360 --> 00:06:18,240
pay the price.

122
00:06:18,480 --> 00:06:19,840
Only by settling regrets

123
00:06:19,840 --> 00:06:22,200
can you return to your own time.

124
00:06:23,320 --> 00:06:26,280
Could it be guiding me?

125
00:06:26,480 --> 00:06:29,800
The original owner's regret is related to the Lu family.

126
00:06:34,400 --> 00:06:35,080
Oh my god,

127
00:06:35,080 --> 00:06:37,000
the Lu family is so rich.

128
00:06:37,960 --> 00:06:40,200
Things I can't afford,

129
00:06:40,200 --> 00:06:43,760
they really stick on the wall.

130
00:06:51,760 --> 00:06:53,760
I can't pry it off.

131
00:06:54,560 --> 00:06:55,840
Anti-addiction.

132
00:06:56,000 --> 00:06:57,920
I am here to find the murderer.

133
00:07:00,760 --> 00:07:02,360
Pearl.

134
00:07:09,000 --> 00:07:10,600
I like it so much.

135
00:07:12,600 --> 00:07:14,600
I don't like it.

136
00:07:14,800 --> 00:07:16,200
I don't like it.

137
00:07:22,680 --> 00:07:25,340
The original owner was killed by someone close.

138
00:07:26,000 --> 00:07:28,200
This family looks a bit strange.

139
00:07:28,200 --> 00:07:32,960
The person who killed the original owner is among them.

140
00:07:34,280 --> 00:07:35,080
Aunt.

141
00:07:35,560 --> 00:07:37,080
Didn't you promise me

142
00:07:37,080 --> 00:07:39,200
that you would kick Shen Zhixia out of the Lu family?

143
00:07:39,200 --> 00:07:40,280
What's the rush?

144
00:07:41,240 --> 00:07:44,360
Many things take time to plan.

145
00:07:45,000 --> 00:07:47,840
The most important thing right now

146
00:07:48,080 --> 00:07:50,640
is to transfer the cooperation with the Shen family

147
00:07:50,640 --> 00:07:52,240
to our Su family.

148
00:07:53,800 --> 00:07:54,600
Jingxi.

149
00:07:54,960 --> 00:07:57,760
You are the main character at tomorrow's banquet.

150
00:07:59,680 --> 00:08:00,360
Mom.

151
00:08:00,600 --> 00:08:02,400
Where did you find this incense?

152
00:08:03,360 --> 00:08:04,160
Jingxi.

153
00:08:04,680 --> 00:08:06,360
Did you hear what I said?

154
00:08:07,880 --> 00:08:08,880
I heard you, Mom.

155
00:08:10,360 --> 00:08:12,520
Just sweet-talk Dad a bit more.

156
00:08:12,600 --> 00:08:14,520
Even if I act first and report later tomorrow.

157
00:08:14,520 --> 00:08:16,050
What can my brother do to me?

158
00:08:18,840 --> 00:08:20,600
Marital discord.

159
00:08:21,400 --> 00:08:26,960
Could Lu Jingheng be the murderer?

160
00:08:50,280 --> 00:08:51,120
What the hell?

161
00:08:51,840 --> 00:08:53,570
Did a thief break into my house?

162
00:08:54,040 --> 00:08:55,200
Or a lecher?

163
00:08:57,440 --> 00:08:58,280
Shen Zhixia.

164
00:08:59,520 --> 00:09:00,400
Are you crazy?

165
00:09:08,240 --> 00:09:09,400
I didn't mean to.

166
00:09:10,760 --> 00:09:11,560
It's you.

167
00:09:15,200 --> 00:09:18,200
He came to sleep with me.

168
00:09:19,040 --> 00:09:20,500
She wants to sleep with me.

169
00:09:21,640 --> 00:09:22,440
Shen Zhixia.

170
00:09:22,560 --> 00:09:24,080
You practiced well.

171
00:09:24,440 --> 00:09:26,500
You have great potential for boxing.

172
00:09:27,640 --> 00:09:28,640
Shen Zhixia.

173
00:09:30,640 --> 00:09:31,440
Shen Zhixia.

174
00:09:38,200 --> 00:09:39,440
I've caught a cold recently.

175
00:09:39,440 --> 00:09:40,200
I'm afraid I'll pass it to you.

176
00:09:40,200 --> 00:09:42,400
Let's sleep in separate rooms tonight.

177
00:09:43,640 --> 00:09:45,100
Please remember clearly.

178
00:09:45,440 --> 00:09:47,640
We won't just sleep in separate rooms today.

179
00:09:47,640 --> 00:09:49,840
We will always sleep in separate rooms.

180
00:09:57,000 --> 00:09:58,330
That scared me to death.

181
00:09:59,440 --> 00:10:01,440
Always sleeping in separate rooms.

182
00:10:04,640 --> 00:10:05,640
If they're on such bad terms,

183
00:10:05,640 --> 00:10:07,100
why did he come to me today?

184
00:10:12,320 --> 00:10:14,280
To deliver medicine.

185
00:10:19,360 --> 00:10:21,080
Could he be the murderer?

